## Key Technical Details

| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| **scrollRef.current** | Stores normalized scroll ratio (0-1) |
| **hasRestoredRef.current** | Prevents multiple restoration attempts |
| **contentReady** | Signals Lexical editor has painted |
| **Double rAF** | Ensures browser paint before scroll calculation |
| **3s debounce** | Prevents excessive API calls while scrolling |
| **UPSERT** | Updates if exists, inserts if new (idempotent) |
| **navigate(path, {replace, state:{}})** | Clears state after using it |
